{"article_id":"OzIl1PItegJlTJ0q","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"( D. , Calif. )","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"speaks during a press briefing in Washington , D.C. , January 17 , 2019 .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"( Joshua Roberts/REUTERS )","depth":2},{"id":4,"text":"It ' s only Tuesday ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"and it feels like a full week already .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"The biggest obstacle to the U.S. House of Representatives","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"impeaching President Trump","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"is Speaker Nancy Pelosi ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"and she ' s refusing to budge ;","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"the Russians cooked up even more ambitious plans","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"to stir up racial hostility in the United States ;","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"and another account from an Obama administration official","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that suggests","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Jim Comey exaggerates","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"and stretches the truth","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"when he wants to make himself look good .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"The Rampart","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"Blocking the Impeachment of Trump","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"Is . . .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"Nancy Pelosi ?","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"At this rate , Nancy Pelosi is going to regret winning the House of Representatives in 2018 :","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Reps. David Cicilline of Rhode Island , Jamie Raskin of Maryland and Joe Neguse of Colorado","depth":15},{"id":23,"text":"- all members of Democratic leadership -","depth":15},{"id":24,"text":"pushed to begin impeachment proceedings during a leadership meeting in Pelosi ' s office ,","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"said the sources .","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"Pelosi and Reps. Rosa DeLauro of Connecticut , Ben Ray Luján of New Mexico , Hakeem Jeffries of New York and Cheri Bustos of Illinois","depth":15},{"id":27,"text":"- some of her key allies -","depth":15},{"id":28,"text":"rejected their calls ,","depth":14},{"id":29,"text":"saying","depth":14},{"id":30,"text":"Democrats ' message is being drowned out by the fight","depth":15},{"id":31,"text":"over possibly impeaching Trump .","depth":15},{"id":32,"text":"Raskin","depth":15},{"id":33,"text":"- a former law professor -","depth":15},{"id":34,"text":"said","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"he wasn ' t advocating impeaching Trump","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"but suggested","depth":15},{"id":37,"text":"that opening an impeachment inquiry would strengthen their legal position","depth":16},{"id":38,"text":"while allowing Democrats to move forward with their legislative agenda .","depth":16},{"id":39,"text":"Pelosi dismissed this argument ,","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"asking Raskin","depth":15},{"id":41,"text":"whether he wanted to shut down the other five committees","depth":17},{"id":42,"text":"working on Trump investigations","depth":17},{"id":43,"text":"in favor of the Judiciary Committee .","depth":16},{"id":44,"text":"\" You want to tell Elijah Cummings to go home ? \"","depth":16},{"id":45,"text":"Pelosi quipped ,","depth":16},{"id":46,"text":"referring to the chairman of the Oversight and Reform Committee .","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"These little anecdotes are reassuring ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"because they indicate to those of us on the right","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"that Democrats don ' t keep all of their condescension , self-righteousness , sneers , disdain , and contempt","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"stored up","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"to use on us .","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"No , this is just how they talk to everyone ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"including each other .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"According to Politico ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Steve Cohen basically called Pelosi a coward to her face .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"During the Steering and Policy Committee meeting , Cohen said","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"President Bill Clinton faced impeachment proceedings \" over sex \"","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"while Trump is \" raping the country , \"","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"according to two sources in the room .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Cohen later confirmed his remarks .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Pelosi pushed back on Cohen during the meeting and his assertion","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"that she was simply afraid impeachment would cost her the House majority .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"\" This isn ' t about politics at all .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"It ' s about patriotism .","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"It ' s about the strength","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"we need","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"to have","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"to see things through , \"","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"Pelosi said ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"according to an aide in the room .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Cohen ' s not alone .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"One of President Obama ' s old HUD guys , Brandon Friedman , is out there","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"proclaiming ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"\" Democrats were sold a bill of goods by Pelosi :","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Vote for us","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"so we can become the majority","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"and hold Trump accountable .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"When voters did that ,","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"the argument became ,","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"' We can ' t hold Trump accountable","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"because it could jeopardize our majority ! ' \"","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"What happens to Pelosi","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"when she ' s opposed by the pro-impeachment Left and the anti-impeachment Right ?","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"New Papers :","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"Russians Wanted to Create African-American Separatist Group for Sabotage","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"This month turned out a good time","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"to be focus on Russian disinformation .","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"NBC News offers a new look at some of the ambitions of the Russians at the Internet Research Agency , beyond the 2016 U.S. elections :","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"The documents","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"- communications between associates of Yevgeny Prigozhin , a Kremlin-linked oligarch","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"indicted by special counsel Robert Mueller for previous influence operations against the U.S. -","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"laid out a new plot","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"to manipulate and radicalize African-Americans .","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"The documents contained proposals for several ways","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"to further exacerbate racial discord in the future ,","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"including a suggestion","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"to recruit African-Americans","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"and transport them to camps in Africa","depth":17},{"id":99,"text":"\" for combat prep and training in sabotage. \"","depth":17},{"id":100,"text":"Those recruits would then be sent back to America","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"to foment violence","depth":17},{"id":102,"text":"and work","depth":17},{"id":103,"text":"to establish a pan-African state in the Southern U.S. ,","depth":17},{"id":104,"text":"including South Carolina , Georgia , Alabama , Mississippi and Louisiana .","depth":17},{"id":105,"text":"There is no indication","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"that the plan","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"- which is light on details -","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"was ever put into action ,","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"but it offers a fresh example of the mindset around Russian efforts","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"to sow discord in the U.S .","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"One aspect of the mindset","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"it reveals","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"is that ethno-nationalists think","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"everyone else sees the world in ethno-nationalist terms .","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"There are roughly 47 million African-Americans in the United States .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"No doubt somewhere in that mix you could find some","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"who be attracted to the idea of a pan-African state","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"spread across five southern states .","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"I ' m not African-American","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"and shouldn ' t presume to know how every member of this group would react .","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"But I suspect","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"quite a few would think ,","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"\" Wait , why would I want that ?","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"I already have a country .","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"I ' ve already put a lot into building my life in this country .","depth":17},{"id":126,"text":"We put a lot of blood , sweat and tears","depth":18},{"id":127,"text":"into ending separate but equal , particularly in those five states !","depth":18},{"id":128,"text":"Why would I want to create my own separate country through violence","depth":15},{"id":129,"text":"instead of trying to change and improve the one","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"I ' m in ? \"","depth":15},{"id":131,"text":"Also note","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"while the Russians were discussing this idea ,","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"they were also promoting the secession of Texas and other Southern states through the Facebook group \" Heart of Texas. \"","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"No doubt ,","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"they would love to see the United States paralyzed by warring internal factions ,","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"each refusing to compromise","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"and attempting to break away .","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"A key point in my talk is that","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"when you ' re trying to differentiate between foreign disinformation or propaganda efforts and genuine homegrown political activism ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"foreign disinformation rarely focuses on any solutions ,","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"when they do ,","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"it ' s the most extreme option .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"A significant portion of the IRA ' s efforts targeted African-Americans","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"and focused on the issue of police brutality and shootings .","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"The examples of Philando Castile , Eric Garner , and Walter Scott make clear","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"when African Americans face an encounter with the police ,","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"they have reason","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"to fear","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"that even the smallest misunderstanding or misstep could have unjust and deadly consequences .","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"But most African-Americans","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"deeply upset about this","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"are thinking about the best way","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"to address it .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"More African-American police officers ?","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"A country","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"where every cop wears a body camera ?","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"Federal civil-rights prosecutions ,","depth":15},{"id":161,"text":"as seen in South Carolina ?","depth":15},{"id":162,"text":"More police training ?","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"Some mix of all of these ?","depth":15},{"id":164,"text":"What you haven ' t heard is African-Americans declaring","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"that the appropriate response is to form their own country .","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"One of my big points in my talk last week was that the Russians at the Internet Research Agency had only studied American culture from a distance .","depth":7},{"id":167,"text":"They ' re trying to manipulate us ,","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"but they don ' t really understand us","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"- and as a result , their efforts are going to be a little clumsy , heavy-handed ,","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"and not quite sound right to American ears .","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"One last point :","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"In addition to his ties to the Internet Research Agency , Yevgeny Prigozhin is also tied to the Wagner Group .","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"Depending upon who you ask ,","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"the Wagner group is a private military contractor like Blackwater , or an off-the-books army of Vladimir Putin ,","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"deploying to places like Ukraine , Syria , Libya , Sudan , and perhaps Venezuela .","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"A murky aura persists around Wagner and the man","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"who is thought to own it .","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"A balding 57-year-old","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"who often manages to be photographed","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"scowling ,","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"Yevgeny Prigozhin is an example of how people close to Putin build their wealth","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"- and then are deployed as useful tools .","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"He was a little-known restaurateur","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"until he appeared in Putin ' s orbit in the early 2000s","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"and began serving the autocrat during visits by foreign dignitaries .","depth":12},{"id":186,"text":"Prigozhin became a powerful businessman","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"as he received a steady stream of catering contracts from the state .","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"Often referred to in the local press as \" Putin ' s chef , \"","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"he is now seen as a key member of Putin ' s inner circle .","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"These perks come with strings attached ,","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"according to Stephen Blank , a Russia expert","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"who has been researching the Wagner Group for the U.S , Army War College .","depth":13},{"id":193,"text":"He sees Prigozhin as an example of how Putin has weaponized Russia ' s wealthy elites .","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"\" They ' re subordinate to the state ,","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"and they keep their money and their positions on the condition","depth":14},{"id":196,"text":"that they serve the state , \"","depth":14},{"id":197,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"Loretta Lynch :","depth":5},{"id":199,"text":"I Never Wanted to Create the Federal Bureau of Matters","depth":5},{"id":200,"text":"Remember Jim Comey ' s anecdote of attorney general Loretta Lynch","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"telling him to refer the investigation of Hillary Clinton as a \" matter \" and not as and \" investigation \" ?","depth":8},{"id":202,"text":"For what it ' s worth ,","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"Lynch says","depth":9},{"id":204,"text":"it didn ' t happen the way","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"Comey described :","depth":9},{"id":206,"text":"Q :","depth":7},{"id":207,"text":"Are you familiar with his","depth":9},{"id":208,"text":"- I think","depth":10},{"id":209,"text":"he ' s testified to this -","depth":10},{"id":210,"text":"that you instructed ,","depth":11},{"id":211,"text":"I believe","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"in September of 2015 ,","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"Director Comey to call the Midyear Exam investigation a matter ?","depth":9},{"id":214,"text":"Lynch :","depth":6},{"id":215,"text":"I heard his testimony on it","depth":7},{"id":216,"text":"and that was the first time","depth":8},{"id":217,"text":"that he had ever indicated to me , in my understanding","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"- he may have told 17 others -","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"that he had that impression of our conversation .","depth":9},{"id":220,"text":"Q :","depth":7},{"id":221,"text":"So you do not believe","depth":8},{"id":222,"text":"you ever instructed him to call it a matter ?","depth":8},{"id":223,"text":"Lynch :","depth":9},{"id":224,"text":"I did not .","depth":9},{"id":225,"text":"I have never instructed a witness as to what to say specifically .","depth":10},{"id":226,"text":"Never have ,","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"never will...","depth":11},{"id":228,"text":"I didn ' t direct anyone to use specific phraseology .","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"When the Director asked me how to best to handle that ,","depth":9},{"id":230,"text":"I said :","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"What I have been saying is we have received a referral","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":"and we are working on the matter ,","depth":13},{"id":233,"text":"working on the issue ,","depth":13},{"id":234,"text":"or we have all the resources","depth":14},{"id":235,"text":"we need","depth":14},{"id":236,"text":"to handle the matter ,","depth":14},{"id":237,"text":"handle the issue .","depth":14},{"id":238,"text":"So that was the suggestion","depth":9},{"id":239,"text":"that I made to him .","depth":9},{"id":240,"text":"Oh , come on .","depth":6},{"id":241,"text":"What are the odds","depth":8},{"id":242,"text":"that Jim Comey would exaggerate or stretch the truth a little","depth":8},{"id":243,"text":"to create a story","depth":8},{"id":244,"text":"that paints him as the last honest man in Washington ?","depth":8},{"id":245,"text":"ADDENDUM :","depth":5},{"id":246,"text":"In case you missed it late yesterday ,","depth":6},{"id":247,"text":"ESPN president Jimmy Pitaro ,","depth":9},{"id":248,"text":"who took over running the network in March 2018 ,","depth":9},{"id":249,"text":"told the Los Angeles Times ,","depth":8},{"id":250,"text":"\" Without question","depth":11},{"id":251,"text":"our data tells us","depth":12},{"id":252,"text":"our fans do not want us to cover politics .","depth":12},{"id":253,"text":"My job is to provide clarity .","depth":10},{"id":254,"text":"I really believe","depth":10},{"id":255,"text":"that some of our talent was confused on what was expected of them .","depth":10},{"id":256,"text":"If you fast-forward to today ,","depth":9},{"id":257,"text":"I don ' t believe","depth":10},{"id":258,"text":"they are confused . \"","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":517,"left":262,"right":516,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":261,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":260,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":260,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":516,"left":455,"right":515,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":455,"left":274,"right":454,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":274,"left":263,"right":273,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":263,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":273,"left":266,"right":272,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":266,"left":265,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":264,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":264,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":267,"right":271,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":267,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":12,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":269,"right":16,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":13,"right":268,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":268,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":454,"left":340,"right":453,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":340,"left":338,"right":339,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":338,"left":327,"right":337,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":327,"left":310,"right":326,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":303,"right":309,"relati